  "detailed_description": "<h1>OUR NEW GAME</h1><p></p><br><h1>JOIN OUR DISCORD!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What is SokoChess Black?</h2>SokoChess Black is a unique chess puzzle game in which you must use your wits to navigate each level, moving, pushing and capturing white pieces until there are none left.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Capture the white pieces</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2482820/extras/b2b87780df4f0068d6d6042165ceb763.poster.avif?t=1757579801\" width=400 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2482820/extras/b2b87780df4f0068d6d6042165ceb763.webm?t=1757579801\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2482820/extras/b2b87780df4f0068d6d6042165ceb763.mp4?t=1757579801\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The goal of each level is to capture all the white pieces.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Move and push your own pieces</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2482820/extras/e4e3292bf8e049a8e7939e4c47f41076.poster.avif?t=1757579801\" width=400 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2482820/extras/e4e3292bf8e049a8e7939e4c47f41076.webm?t=1757579801\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2482820/extras/e4e3292bf8e049a8e7939e4c47f41076.mp4?t=1757579801\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You can move your own pieces but also push them to make them move in a way they normally couldn't.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Beyond Chess</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2482820/extras/ef77605c0734b47a077e47ec68f3a7eb.poster.avif?t=1757579801\" width=450 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2482820/extras/ef77605c0734b47a077e47ec68f3a7eb.webm?t=1757579801\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2482820/extras/ef77605c0734b47a077e47ec68f3a7eb.mp4?t=1757579801\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Overcome many unique obstacles before unseen in Chess!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2482820/extras/f07a4af4500ac67319d6dfaa42a53ebc.avif?t=1757579801\" width=620 height=85 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 70 handcrafted levels<br></li><li> Infinite undos<br></li><li> Puzzle elements you won't see in Chess<br></li><li> Don't like a level you are playing? Skip it!<br></li><li> Unique gameplay combining Chess and Sokoban</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Experience Chess like never before!</h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What is SokoChess Black?</h2>SokoChess Black is a unique chess puzzle game in which you must use your wits to navigate each level, moving, pushing and capturing white pieces until there are none left.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Capture the white pieces</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2482820/extras/b2b87780df4f0068d6d6042165ceb763.poster.avif?t=1757579801\" width=400 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2482820/extras/b2b87780df4f0068d6d6042165ceb763.webm?t=1757579801\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2482820/extras/b2b87780df4f0068d6d6042165ceb763.mp4?t=1757579801\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The goal of each level is to capture all the white pieces.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Move and push your own pieces</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2482820/extras/e4e3292bf8e049a8e7939e4c47f41076.poster.avif?t=1757579801\" width=400 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2482820/extras/e4e3292bf8e049a8e7939e4c47f41076.webm?t=1757579801\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2482820/extras/e4e3292bf8e049a8e7939e4c47f41076.mp4?t=1757579801\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You can move your own pieces but also push them to make them move in a way they normally couldn't.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Beyond Chess</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2482820/extras/ef77605c0734b47a077e47ec68f3a7eb.poster.avif?t=1757579801\" width=450 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2482820/extras/ef77605c0734b47a077e47ec68f3a7eb.webm?t=1757579801\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2482820/extras/ef77605c0734b47a077e47ec68f3a7eb.mp4?t=1757579801\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Overcome many unique obstacles before unseen in Chess!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2482820/extras/f07a4af4500ac67319d6dfaa42a53ebc.avif?t=1757579801\" width=620 height=85 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 70 handcrafted levels<br></li><li> Infinite undos<br></li><li> Puzzle elements you won't see in Chess<br></li><li> Don't like a level you are playing? Skip it!<br></li><li> Unique gameplay combining Chess and Sokoban</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Experience Chess like never before!</h2>",
